        <p>The WZPDCL Prepaid Token Extractor application, including its code, design, and content, is available as open-source software. You may view, fork, and contribute to the code on <a href="https://github.com/anupdebnath/wzpdcl-prepaid-token-extractor" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
